  "stem": "<p>The function <em>g</em> is defined by <math><mi>g</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></math>. Which table gives three values of <em>x</em> and their corresponding values of <em>g(x)</em>?</p>",
